text: Magdalene Epply-Staudinger (born 22 September 1910, date of death unknown) was an Austrian diver. She competed in two events at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Austrian female divers Category:Olympic divers of Austria Category:Divers at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
